  "verification_notes": "Ed Cooley completed his 3rd season as head coach. Hoyas finished 16-18 (6-14 Big East, 10th place, 11 seed in Big East Tournament). Started 5-0 (program's best start since 2017-18). Upset DePaul and Villanova in Big East Tournament before losing to #6 UConn 51-67 in semifinals. Did NOT make NCAA Tournament. Georgetown plays home games primarily at Capital One Arena with select games at on-campus McDonough Gymnasium. Capital One Arena capacity (20,356) is the standard arena basketball capacity; effective Georgetown capacity may be configured lower. Ed Cooley's career record and tenure record not specifically verified — left null. Lee Reed in his 9th year as Georgetown AD. Roster shown is 2025-26 season-end. 2026-27 schedule TBD.",
